|---|---|
| `job/data-sync-job` | **NotFound** ✅ |
| `pod/data-sync-job-pod` | **NotFound** ✅ |
| `pvc/data-sync-storage` | **Bound** — preserved ✅ |
| `secret/db-credentials` | **Present** — preserved ✅ |
